channel.title: Ekstrak - Free Picture Designer!
channel.description:
Now that I wait until May for my end-of-the-year school testing to end so that I can get back to making music, I decided to take to their hobbies. One of them is art. I’m very good at that.
That’s why I’m taking free art requests, no matter how crazy, detailed, or simple it is.
